    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. Mesh independence confirmed with GCI below 5%. NIH predictions agree with FDA benchmark within 15% MARE. RH < 1.0 for all geometric variants satisfies the pre-specified acceptance criterion. The CFD model is assessed as sufficiently credible to support the regulatory decision on worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
